\c 75
\s Rwiyo rwokuvonga Mwari
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weAritasheti. Pisarema raAsafi.
\s Rwiyo.
\p
\v 1 Tinokuvongai, Mwari; Tinovonga, nokuti zita renyu riri pedyo;
\s Vanhu vanoparidza mabasa enyu anoshamisa.
\p
\v 2 "Kana ndichiwana nguva yakafanira,
\s Ndichatonga zvakarurama.
\p
\v 3 Pasi pose panyauka navose vagerepo;
\s Ndini ndakamisa mbiru dzayo.
\p
\v 4 Ndakati. huka Nax‘a. max‘yami, `Regai kuita namanyawi;' Nokuna vakaipa,
\s `Regai kusimudza runyanga.'
\p
\v 5 Regai kusimudza runyanga rwenyu kudenga;
\s Regai kutaura nomutsipa mukukutu."
\p
\v 6 Nokuti kunyange kumabudazuva, kana kumavirira,
\s Kana kurenje, hakuzi ikoko kunobva kukudzwa.
\p
\v 7 Asi Mwari ndiye mutongi; Anoninipisa mumwe achikudza mumwe.
\p
\v 8 Nokuti muruoko rwaJehovha munomukombe, newaini inopupuma;
\s Uzere nezvakavhenganiswa, zvino anodurura mauri;
\s Zvirokwazvo, vakaipa vose venyika vachasvina masese awo, nokuanwa.
\p
\v 9 Asi ini ndichaparidza nokusingaperi,
\s Ndichaimbira Mwari waJakobho nziyo dzokurumbidza.
\p
\v 1 ° Nyanga dzose dzavakaipa ndichadzigura;
\s Asi nyanga dzavakarurama dzichasimudzwa.
